---
// Spanish variant of Quickstart.astro.
// Install commands and CLI output stay English (literal command strings + stdout).
---

<section class="quickstart section" id="quickstart" aria-labelledby="quickstart-title">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 id="quickstart-title" class="quickstart__title">
      ¿Prefieres la CLI?
    </h2>
    <p class="quickstart__lede">
      ¿No usas agentes de IA, o necesitas validación de specs en tu
      pipeline de CI? Hay una CLI para eso. Se instala en 60 segundos
      — sin cuenta, sin telemetría, funciona en cualquier carpeta de
      specs en Markdown.
    </p>

    <div class="qs-tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="Comando de instalación para tu sistema operativo">
      <button
        type="button"
        role="tab"
        id="qs-tab-unix"
        aria-controls="qs-panel-unix"
        aria-selected="true"
        tabindex="0"
        class="qs-tab is-active"
        data-tab="unix"
      >
        Linux / macOS
      </button>
      <button
        type="button"
        role="tab"
        id="qs-tab-windows"
        aria-controls="qs-panel-windows"
        aria-selected="false"
        tabindex="-1"
        class="qs-tab"
        data-tab="windows"
      >
        Windows
      </button>
    </div>

    <div
      id="qs-panel-unix"
      role="tabpanel"
      aria-labelledby="qs-tab-unix"
      class="qs-panel is-active"
      data-panel="unix"
    >
<pre class="terminal"><span class="prompt">$</span> curl -fsSL https://specscore.md/install/get-cli | sh</pre>
    </div>

    <div
      id="qs-panel-windows"
      role="tabpanel"
      aria-labelledby="qs-tab-windows"
      class="qs-panel"
      data-panel="windows"
      hidden
    >
<pre class="terminal"><span class="prompt">&gt;</span> irm https://specscore.md/install/get-cli.ps1 | iex</pre>
    </div>

    <p class="quickstart__step">
      Pasa el linter a la spec de ejemplo que viene con el binario:
    </p>
<pre class="terminal terminal--window"><span class="prompt">$</span> specscore lint examples/checkout/apply-discount.md</pre>

    <p class="quickstart__step">Mira la salida:</p>
<pre class="terminal terminal--window">  examples/checkout/apply-discount.md
    <span class="mark-pass">✓</span> R1  Single-code limit
    <span class="mark-pass">✓</span> R2  Code validity
    <span class="mark-fail">✗</span> R3  Discount application
         <span class="dim">AC-3:18</span>  ambiguous AC — "higher-of rule" doesn't specify the tiebreaker
                  <span class="dim">fix:</span> specify "higher discount wins; if tied, site-wide promotion wins"

  <span class="dim">1 of 3 requirements failing</span>
  <span class="dim">exit 1</span></pre>

    <p class="quickstart__next">
      Lee la <a class="xref" href="/docs">documentación completa</a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <a class="xref" href="https://github.com/specscore/specscore">Contribuye en GitHub</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<script is:inline>
  (function () {
    var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.qs-tab');
    var panels = document.querySelectorAll('.qs-panel');
    if (!tabs.length) return;

    function activate(name, focus) {
      tabs.forEach(function (t) {
        var on = t.getAttribute('data-tab') === name;
        t.classList.toggle('is-active', on);
        t.setAttribute('aria-selected', on ? 'true' : 'false');
        t.setAttribute('tabindex', on ? '0' : '-1');
        if (on && focus) t.focus();
      });
      panels.forEach(function (p) {
        var on = p.getAttribute('data-panel') === name;
        p.classList.toggle('is-active', on);
        if (on) p.removeAttribute('hidden');
        else p.setAttribute('hidden', '');
      });
    }

    // Auto-detect: Windows users see Windows tab by default. Otherwise default
    // remains Linux/macOS as rendered server-side. Keyboard users can still
    // switch — auto-detect changes the visual default, not the focusable order.
    try {
      if (/Windows/i.test(navigator.userAgent)) {
        activate('windows', false);
      }
    } catch (e) {
      /* ignore */
    }

    tabs.forEach(function (tab) {
      tab.addEventListener('click', function () {
        activate(tab.getAttribute('data-tab'), false);
      });
      tab.addEventListener('keydown', function (ev) {
        var key = ev.key;
        if (key !== 'ArrowRight' && key !== 'ArrowLeft' &&
            key !== 'Home' && key !== 'End') return;
        ev.preventDefault();
        var i = Array.prototype.indexOf.call(tabs, ev.currentTarget);
        var next;
        if (key === 'ArrowRight') next = (i + 1) % tabs.length;
        else if (key === 'ArrowLeft') next = (i - 1 + tabs.length) % tabs.length;
        else if (key === 'Home') next = 0;
        else next = tabs.length - 1;
        activate(tabs[next].getAttribute('data-tab'), true);
      });
    });
  })();
</script>

<style>
  .quickstart { background: var(--cream); }
  .quickstart__title {
    font-size: var(--fs-h2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .quickstart__lede {
    color: var(--mid-ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .qs-tabs {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .qs-tab {
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    padding: 0.55rem 0.95rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--mid-ink);
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    margin-bottom: -1px;
    transition: color 120ms ease, border-color 120ms ease;
  }
  .qs-tab:hover {
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .qs-tab.is-active {
    color: var(--ink);
    border-bottom-color: var(--validator-green);
  }
  .qs-tab:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--ink-blue);
    outline-offset: 2px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .qs-panel {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .qs-panel pre {
    border-top-width: 0;
  }

  .quickstart__step {
    margin: var(--space-3) 0 var(--space-2);
    color: var(--mid-ink);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .quickstart__next {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--mid-ink);
  }
</style>
